You need to download the repository and run it in Visual Stuido 8, if .NET 8 is missing, install it. If necessary, download the necessary packages from the nuget repository

The application must be launched in a browser. If swagger does not start, enter /swagger after the localhost address. We will then get a list of available endpoints

